Reptilica is a male, Logo. The name might sound feminine, but I didn't name 
him.

::Reptilica/DevilDuer::

Reptilica nods. "Follow me," he says, walking off toward the Alliance base.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
In the bushes, DevilDuer narrows his eyes, carefully aiming his gun at 
Feline's head. He fires a stun dart, the shot heading for the female's neck. 
If it hits, it would send electric waves through the bot, rendering it 
unconscious for several hours.
